Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你句這種場合常用的經典台詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉有用的話還要警察幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧的這麼大 結果還是讓目標Talisman跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不該跟什麼警察合作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Talisman有犯罪嫌疑這點是確實的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是無法對這點視若無睹才會幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Spooky Boogie 無政府主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼我絕對不會再幫助你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友誼產生裂痕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 本來跟她也就只是同學關係而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不知道她到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的對話有記錄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~OP~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:09.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰にも見せられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:09.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦內充斥著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:14.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭の中溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:14.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法為他人所道之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:20.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間違いさえもない世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:20.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.21,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷い込んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連絲毫差錯也無的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありえないほど吸い込まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸進不可置信的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目に見えるものだけの世界現象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這滿溢只為肉眼所見事物的世界現象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:40.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴き出せるか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:40.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否將其揭露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plastic　Plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plastic　Plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:46.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　誰もおかしくなれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:46.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 誰也不會變得奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.21,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴様もPlastic in for World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只不過是Plastic in for World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:55.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美しすぎる世界に僕は何故か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:55.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這美得過於炫目的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光が見えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何我卻看不見光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅列していく心が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那陳列在外的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限のReflection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是無限的Reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:10.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,secret kills for you secret kills for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:10.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,secret kills for you secret kills for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,secret image for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,secret image for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:25.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見せかけの色で 未来を暴かないで
